ote>收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n呢種頭2012,13年果陣梳<br />\n果陣EURO USA果邊都慢慢多人咁梳既時候<br />\n香港人又問你做咩事咁既頭<br />\n身邊D女又話個頭做咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過多兩年三年呢?<br />\n一街都係, 多人梳, 又變左開始讚D人換左咁樣好睇<br />\n<br />\n咁OK 多人係咁既頭冇問題, 唔係咩專利野<br />\n<br />\n但係當有D人行得前少少果陣<br />\n你又咪笑柒人, 個頭咩事?<br />\n一樣野變左大眾野, 你又笑人普通<br />\n有人行緊最前面, lead緊, 又笑人獨特<br />\n點滿足你地呢種多管閒事既人呀你話?</blockquote><br />\n我梳咗呢種髮型都好多年（唔識gel飛輪海頭）"},{"pid":"0d40898e5cf53ce4f7f23a021f435fa772c35bc7","tid":491661,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57cbdfe0885be4f53dc2d93e096516898fedd0f3","tid":491661,"uid":21222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留陰又話Mk，Gel起又話老土<br />\n樓主你又咩髮型，想見識下你與眾不同嘅頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y4Cgoii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy4Cgoii.jpg&h=3864111d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你一講外型衣著就出呢張大絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無得討論嫁喎"},{"pid":"b0cffe1b32b2817f40096abbb658faf120b4fd03","tid":491661,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留陰又話Mk，Gel起又話老土<br />\n樓主你又咩髮型，想見識下你與眾不同嘅頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y4Cgoii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy4Cgoii.jpg&h=3864111d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n六四分界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019addc40a82a340737dbfdcefb9133b14e11879","tid":491661,"uid":139473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"貼返啲新既潮童圖至得架"},{"pid":"6e50e604740b51a53fef91bc094b049b70e990e6","tid":491661,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:44:08.000Z","msg":